modifier.nyx.feint.desc=§oFaster than the speed of light!§r\nYour tool has a 20% chance to deal an additional +25% damage while also gaining the ability to pierce through armor.
modifier.nyx.frezarites_bane.name=Frezarite's Bane
modifier.nyx.frezarites_bane.desc=§oIt's a nuclear winter!§r\nSuccessful hits greatly slows your target more and more.
modifier.nyx.glacier.name=Glacier
modifier.nyx.glacier.desc=§oPK Freeze!§r\nAll attacks will cause a small explosion that deals area of effect damage. All affected mobs will also become inflicted with Slowness III for a few seconds.
modifier.nyx.gleaming.name=Gleaming
