modifier.nyx.hypercharge.desc=§oMaximum power!§r\nHitting a target or breaking a block has a chance to charge you up with Haste IV and Strength II for a few seconds!
modifier.nyx.kreknorites_bane.name=Kreknorite's Bane
modifier.nyx.kreknorites_bane.desc=§oThe Nether right at your doorstep!§r\nSuccessful hits greatly withers your target more and more. The target will also be set on fire.
modifier.nyx.stunlock.name=Stunlock
modifier.nyx.stunlock.desc=§oStay put!§r\nHit targets have a chance to become stunned and be completely immobile for a few seconds.
modifier.nyx.supercharge.name=Supercharge
modifier.nyx.supercharge.desc=§oSupercharge me!§r\nHitting a target or breaking a block has a chance to charge you up with Haste III for a few seconds!
modifier.nyx.volcano.name=Volcano
modifier.nyx.volcano.desc=§oDid somebody say boom?!§r\nAll attacks will cause a small explosion that deals area of effect damage. All affected mobs will also be set on fire and become inflicted with Wither II.

